.TH Convert Media "07 Sep 1993" "SunSoft" "ToolTalk ICCCM"
.SH NAME
.PP
Convert \- convert an X11 selection
.SH SYNOPSIS
.so ../.synopsis
[\fIfile\f(CW]	Convert(	in	selection	\fIselname\f(CW,	
		in	integer	\fIitem\f(CW,	
		out	\fItarget	data\f(CW );
.ft
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.LP
Instruct a selection owner to convert it to the specified target and
return the data.
.SH REQUIRED ARGUMENTS
.TP
\f(CWselection\fR \fIselname\fR
The selection to be converted.
.TP
\f(CWinteger\fR \fIitem\fR
The part of the disjoint selection to be displayed or edited.  Items
are numbered from 0.  -1 means all the items in the selection.
.TP
.I target data
The converted data.
.I target
is the name of the target to convert.
.SH SEE ALSO
.PP
.BR Intro (Desktop),
.BR Status (Desktop),
.BR Intro (Media)
.SH BUGS
.PP
Needs timestamp?
